summary: An Ordinance approving the assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 1846, for the improvement of Occidental Avenue, from Connecticut Street to Holgate Street, and Atlantic Street and Massachusetts Street, each from Occidental Avenue to First Avenue South, all in the City of Seattle, by filling the same, under Ordinance No. 19149, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against each parcel and lot of land and part thereof shown in said roll, and providing for the collection thereof.
